this is what strenght, agility, intelligence and hero base stats are.


if Primary stats is str, agi or int you will gain 0.20 damage per point
all hero will have 100 life and 100 mana base start

Strenght
life 5
life regeneration 0.04
life 1% for every 10 point of str

Agility
attack speed 0.50
damage 1% for every 10 point of agility

Intelligence
mana 10
mana-regeneration 0.08
spell amp 1% for every 10 point of intelligence

DIVINE STATS after one stats got at least 10,15,20,25,30 base agi,int,str you can spend a Divine Stats into it gaining new bonus
these divine stats can be only be gain every level 10,20,30,40,50 of base stats having a total of 5 to spend.

DIVINE Strenght
armor 1
magic resist 3%
life 5%

DIVINE Agility
give physical spell 2% chance to crit for 130% of the normal damage
attackspeed 5
evasion 2%

DIVINE Intelligence
give magic spell 2% chance to crit for 130% of the normal damage
spell amp 3%
mana 5%

-NOTE- if people have crit spell or crit physical the % chance will stack on it meaning the 2% will go on a 10% and have a crit
for a total of 12%
